---
By: Han Shan
Source:
  ISBN: 1556591403
  Page: 237
  Publisher: Copper Canyon Press
  Title: The Collected Songs of Cold Mountain
  Translator: Red Pine
---
Today I sat before the cliffs
I sat until the mist drew off
a single crystal stream
a towering ridge of jade
a cloud's dawn shadown not yet moving
the moon's night light still adrift
a body free of dust
a mind without care
